Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:29.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,向着顶点前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.65,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}We must be the change we wish to see...
